1
00:00:30,950 --> 00:00:35,940
♪Your secret, dangerous flaws♪

2
00:00:36,250 --> 00:00:41,620
♪I can stay close
without seeing through♪

3
00:00:41,890 --> 00:00:45,610
♪As long as it's about love♪

4
00:00:45,710 --> 00:00:46,870
♪No matter how absurd♪

5
00:00:47,260 --> 00:00:51,450
♪I choose to get used to it♪

6
00:00:52,810 --> 00:00:56,900
♪Truth or lies, you decide what's true♪

7
00:00:56,970 --> 00:01:00,800
♪I won't overturn it anymore♪

8
00:01:01,040 --> 00:01:03,690
♪I cover my eyes and look♪

9
00:01:03,820 --> 00:01:07,860
♪Is love an abyss or a trap♪

10
00:01:07,960 --> 00:01:14,710
♪I only see the sparkle♪

11
00:01:33,220 --> 00:01:37,980
=Turbulent Love=

12
00:01:38,100 --> 00:01:41,940
=Episode 18=
=If I Could Hate You=

13
00:02:02,680 --> 00:02:04,640
Tonight's event
is your first time attending.

14
00:02:04,760 --> 00:02:05,710
You'd better perform well.

15
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:08,030
I'll just focus on looking pretty.

16
00:02:09,910 --> 00:02:11,240
What should I wear later?

17
00:02:16,590 --> 00:02:17,470
Miss Hao.

18
00:02:18,100 --> 00:02:19,960
Even if you hate me,
don't play ghost to scare me.

19
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:23,560
Miss Zhu, please have some tea.

20
00:02:35,630 --> 00:02:39,000
I'll do anything you ask from now on,
Miss Zhu.

21
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:43,150
Feihu and Xiaocui have paid the price.

22
00:02:44,710 --> 00:02:47,000
Please just spare their lives.

23
00:02:49,100 --> 00:02:50,520
If you had acted like this that day,

24
00:02:51,200 --> 00:02:52,430
this wouldn't have happened today.

25
00:02:57,710 --> 00:02:58,590
Tonight,

26
00:02:58,960 --> 00:02:59,870
Ji Zhijie and I are going

27
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:01,750
to an important party.

28
00:03:02,030 --> 00:03:03,630
We'll discuss our engagement.

29
00:03:05,710 --> 00:03:07,870
You can hang up my clothes later

30
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:09,560
and then help me get dressed.

31
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:12,680
Okay.

32
00:04:22,450 --> 00:04:23,300
You're so clumsy.

33
00:04:23,310 --> 00:04:24,240
What are you even good for?

34
00:04:30,310 --> 00:04:31,510
If there's nothing else,

35
00:04:32,750 --> 00:04:33,800
I'll get back to work.

36
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:37,270
What trick are you playing now?

37
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:38,440
Hao Yu?

38
00:04:42,430 --> 00:04:44,270
What trick could I possibly play?

39
00:04:45,920 --> 00:04:48,160
I dragged Xiaocui and Feihu into this.

40
00:04:48,190 --> 00:04:50,390
I'm already drowning in guilt.

41
00:04:54,390 --> 00:04:56,680
I knelt but you wouldn't calm down.

42
00:04:58,000 --> 00:05:00,070
So I could only beg Miss Zhu

43
00:05:01,120 --> 00:05:03,240
to spare Xiaocui and Feihu.

44
00:05:04,560 --> 00:05:05,400
Or at the very least,

45
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:08,270
let them die with dignity.

46
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:15,750
Hao Yu, listen.

47
00:05:17,240 --> 00:05:18,240
This is the most crucial time

48
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:20,070
for my deal with the councilor.

49
00:05:20,430 --> 00:05:21,600
If you ruin anything

50
00:05:21,870 --> 00:05:23,000
because of you,

51
00:05:23,630 --> 00:05:24,800
I'll make you suffer.

52
00:05:25,270 --> 00:05:26,160
Do you understand?

53
00:05:30,390 --> 00:05:31,230
After tonight.

54
00:05:32,310 --> 00:05:33,150
Yes.

55
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:36,080
Tonight.

56
00:05:37,510 --> 00:05:38,560
As long as you behave

57
00:05:38,600 --> 00:05:39,720
and stay out of trouble,

58
00:05:41,430 --> 00:05:42,480
I will let you go.

59
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:46,920
You'll be free.

60
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:49,760
Is tonight

61
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:53,360
some kind of special day?

62
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:00,920
Just remember what I said.

63
00:06:04,750 --> 00:06:05,590
Behave.

64
00:06:52,560 --> 00:06:53,720
Hello, Miss Hao.

65
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:56,160
You finally agreed to work with me.

66
00:06:58,830 --> 00:06:59,720
Li Minglang?

67
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:01,760
Yeah.

68
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:02,760
It's me.

69
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:06,190
You know Xiaocui?

70
00:07:07,830 --> 00:07:09,040
You two are partners, right?

71
00:07:10,480 --> 00:07:11,390
She's your informant?

72
00:07:14,600 --> 00:07:15,950
You're Mr. Guan's goddaughter,

73
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:18,040
so you should know the basics.

74
00:07:18,870 --> 00:07:20,680
Normally I wouldn't answer that.

75
00:07:22,070 --> 00:07:23,600
But since Xiaocui is gone.

76
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:26,510
She wasn't my informant.

77
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:27,440
She was a reporter.

78
00:07:27,950 --> 00:07:29,070
We just worked together.

79
00:07:35,870 --> 00:07:36,800
You called me.

80
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:38,360
So do you have any news about Xiaocui?

81
00:07:41,830 --> 00:07:43,160
Xiaocui told me everything.

82
00:07:44,390 --> 00:07:45,680
She left me a note.

83
00:07:45,720 --> 00:07:46,720
Telling me to contact you.

84
00:07:49,190 --> 00:07:50,040
But I'm sorry.

85
00:07:51,310 --> 00:07:52,560
I just can't trust you.

86
00:07:54,720 --> 00:07:56,240
But I'll finish the task Xiaocui gave me

87
00:07:56,920 --> 00:07:58,480
in my own way.

88
00:08:02,800 --> 00:08:04,360
If you want to work with me,

89
00:08:05,360 --> 00:08:06,600
you have to follow my lead.

90
00:08:08,040 --> 00:08:10,000
I won't let anyone control me now.

91
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:15,000
I don't know if you're good or bad.

92
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:18,000
So

93
00:08:18,680 --> 00:08:19,720
I have my own plan.

94
00:08:20,390 --> 00:08:21,830
Just follow my plan.

95
00:08:24,040 --> 00:08:25,120
What do you need me to do?

96
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:27,440
Just wait for my word.

97
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:36,440
Hurry up.

98
00:08:36,550 --> 00:08:37,600
Godfather hates waiting.

99
00:08:38,150 --> 00:08:39,150
Who are the others?

100
00:08:40,240 --> 00:08:41,080
These lists

101
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:43,080
rotate on a ranking elimination basis.

102
00:08:43,240 --> 00:08:46,240
Just state governors,
police station chiefs,

103
00:08:46,550 --> 00:08:47,750
and a few big shots.

104
00:08:55,550 --> 00:08:56,390
Look.

105
00:08:56,870 --> 00:08:58,870
(Tingfeng Pavilion, Tea Art Park)
This is the place

106
00:08:59,030 --> 00:08:59,870
your former Cangfeng boss

107
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:01,030
could never get into.

108
00:09:03,390 --> 00:09:04,840
Now you're so young.

109
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:06,630
Let's go. You can enter now.

110
00:09:10,340 --> 00:09:16,380
(Tea Art Park)

111
00:09:49,550 --> 00:09:50,750
Hurry up with the project.

112
00:09:52,630 --> 00:09:53,470
You're here.

113
00:09:58,600 --> 00:09:59,840
Welcome our new friend.

114
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:06,240
I propose a toast.

115
00:10:06,870 --> 00:10:07,710
Come on.

116
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:10,150
Cangfeng Group officially
signs a cooperation agreement

117
00:10:10,290 --> 00:10:12,030
with the Li Island Development Agency
today.

118
00:10:12,150 --> 00:10:15,120
Mr. Ji Zhijie and
Miss Zhu Shuyi's marriage

119
00:10:15,200 --> 00:10:16,900
was also confirmed by Councilman Zhu.

120
00:10:16,900 --> 00:10:17,740
(Cangfeng & Li Island
New Plan Signing)

121
00:10:17,740 --> 00:10:18,780
Mr. Ji, look here.

122
00:10:18,790 --> 00:10:19,750
Miss Zhu, look here.

123
00:10:19,840 --> 00:10:20,680
Mr. Ji.

124
00:10:20,910 --> 00:10:21,750
Mr. Ji.

125
00:10:21,750 --> 00:10:24,300
(Ji Zhijie and Zhu Shuyi's
marriage confirmed)

126
00:10:27,480 --> 00:10:28,320
Congratulations.

127
00:10:28,480 --> 00:10:29,320
Congrats. Congrats.

128
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:30,360
Congratulations.

129
00:10:31,700 --> 00:10:32,540
Here.

130
00:10:32,630 --> 00:10:33,470
Mr. Zhu.

131
00:10:33,760 --> 00:10:34,600
Please look here.

132
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:35,910
- Mr. Zhu, look here.
- Okay.

133
00:10:35,910 --> 00:10:36,780
Congratulations.

134
00:10:36,790 --> 00:10:37,630
Mr. Ji.

135
00:10:38,320 --> 00:10:39,160
Miss Zhu, here.

136
00:10:48,120 --> 00:10:49,870
No wonder you let me go.

137
00:11:00,360 --> 00:11:01,200
Zhijie.

138
00:11:01,360 --> 00:11:02,550
That Miss Hao of yours

139
00:11:03,320 --> 00:11:04,600
isn't very obedient.

140
00:11:07,600 --> 00:11:08,630
Women like her

141
00:11:09,390 --> 00:11:10,870
are nothing but trouble.

142
00:11:11,670 --> 00:11:13,870
Better get rid of her early.

143
00:11:16,270 --> 00:11:17,320
If you want to join us,

144
00:11:17,530 --> 00:11:19,030
you need to prove your loyalty first.

145
00:11:19,790 --> 00:11:20,960
If you can't bear to hurt her,

146
00:11:21,080 --> 00:11:21,960
we'll do it for you.

147
00:11:27,270 --> 00:11:28,670
She's just a woman.

148
00:11:30,080 --> 00:11:31,320
No need to trouble yourselves.

149
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:38,280
This toast

150
00:11:39,550 --> 00:11:41,120
is to the greater good.

151
00:11:53,670 --> 00:11:55,000
Smart man.

152
00:11:56,240 --> 00:11:58,720
Come, to the greater good!

153
00:11:59,080 --> 00:12:00,050
- Come.
- Cheers.

154
00:12:10,670 --> 00:12:11,510
Feilong.

155
00:12:14,750 --> 00:12:15,590
Feiying.

156
00:12:17,910 --> 00:12:18,750
Feihu.

157
00:12:20,080 --> 00:12:20,920
Water...

158
00:12:35,200 --> 00:12:36,040
Water...

159
00:12:37,080 --> 00:12:37,920
Water...

160
00:12:41,550 --> 00:12:42,390
Feilong.

161
00:12:44,720 --> 00:12:45,560
Feilong.

162
00:12:47,510 --> 00:12:48,350
Water.

163
00:13:14,200 --> 00:13:15,390
The workers are on holiday.

164
00:13:16,080 --> 00:13:16,960
Feilong, Feihu, Feiying.

165
00:13:16,970 --> 00:13:18,030
You drove them all away too.

166
00:13:20,150 --> 00:13:21,150
As for Miss Zhu,

167
00:13:21,800 --> 00:13:22,840
I don't know where she is.

168
00:13:29,000 --> 00:13:29,840
Leave.

169
00:13:32,000 --> 00:13:33,000
All of you, leave.

170
00:13:35,120 --> 00:13:35,960
Leave.

171
00:13:38,670 --> 00:13:39,510
You too.

172
00:13:43,320 --> 00:13:45,600
Hao Yu, I can finally let you go.

173
00:13:48,840 --> 00:13:50,630
Finally, I can let you go.

174
00:13:52,600 --> 00:13:53,440
Finally...

175
00:14:00,510 --> 00:14:01,350
You have a fever.

176
00:14:04,320 --> 00:14:05,530
Don't you hate me?

177
00:14:06,290 --> 00:14:07,840
Why do you still care if I live or die?

178
00:14:15,140 --> 00:14:17,390
Stop pretending to be nice to me, okay?

179
00:14:24,390 --> 00:14:25,240
Just go.

180
00:14:28,270 --> 00:14:29,110
Leave.

181
00:14:35,360 --> 00:14:36,910
If you don't leave, I can't promise...

182
00:15:08,120 --> 00:15:08,960
Leave.

183
00:15:12,750 --> 00:15:13,590
Leave!

184
00:15:15,510 --> 00:15:16,670
All of you, leave!

185
00:15:18,630 --> 00:15:19,790
All of you, leave.

186
00:15:56,600 --> 00:15:57,720
I'll have your changed clothes

187
00:15:57,870 --> 00:15:59,440
sent to the dry cleaner later.

188
00:16:03,200 --> 00:16:04,480
And I'll bring them back to you.

189
00:16:10,080 --> 00:16:11,360
You're acting so strange today.

190
00:16:11,600 --> 00:16:12,670
Being nice to me out of nowhere.

191
00:16:18,600 --> 00:16:19,510
Miss Zhu.

192
00:16:20,480 --> 00:16:22,440
I need a favor from you right now.

193
00:16:22,720 --> 00:16:24,320
So I have to swallow my pride.

194
00:16:25,360 --> 00:16:26,200
Besides,

195
00:16:26,670 --> 00:16:28,670
given my current situation,

196
00:16:29,960 --> 00:16:31,510
I can't do anything to you anyway.

197
00:16:33,120 --> 00:16:33,960
That's true.

198
00:16:34,550 --> 00:16:35,420
Now,

199
00:16:35,420 --> 00:16:37,240
we're in very different positions.

200
00:16:37,960 --> 00:16:38,960
I have my godfather.

201
00:16:39,480 --> 00:16:41,200
And Ji Zhijie also has my back.

202
00:16:41,810 --> 00:16:42,910
You wouldn't dare try anything.

203
00:16:44,150 --> 00:16:45,390
Otherwise, as you've seen.

204
00:16:45,550 --> 00:16:47,390
Like Feihu and Xiaocui's

205
00:16:47,480 --> 00:16:48,360
ending.

206
00:16:49,320 --> 00:16:51,600
Be careful, you might be next.

207
00:16:53,790 --> 00:16:56,510
You look really great today.

208
00:16:57,790 --> 00:16:58,630
But...

209
00:16:59,210 --> 00:17:00,550
It feels like something's missing.

210
00:17:00,960 --> 00:17:01,870
A manicure.

211
00:17:05,310 --> 00:17:06,150
You can do that?

212
00:17:08,880 --> 00:17:09,720
My own work.

213
00:17:32,720 --> 00:17:33,920
Let me moisturize your hands.

214
00:17:47,680 --> 00:17:48,520
All done.

215
00:17:54,680 --> 00:17:56,440
Miss Zhu, if there's nothing else,

216
00:17:56,550 --> 00:17:58,000
I'll get back to work.

217
00:17:59,000 --> 00:17:59,840
Go ahead.

218
00:18:14,720 --> 00:18:15,560
Mr. Li.

219
00:18:16,900 --> 00:18:17,920
What brings you here today?

220
00:18:18,000 --> 00:18:18,840
Police inspection.

221
00:18:23,330 --> 00:18:24,590
Any suspicious people around lately?

222
00:18:24,610 --> 00:18:25,500
We run a legit business.

223
00:18:25,550 --> 00:18:26,590
What suspicious person?

224
00:18:26,640 --> 00:18:27,480
No one at all.

225
00:19:06,920 --> 00:19:07,880
Access granted.

226
00:19:42,160 --> 00:19:44,400
I wondered why you were so nice to me.

227
00:19:45,000 --> 00:19:46,310
Doing my nails.

228
00:19:46,680 --> 00:19:48,070
And dry-cleaning my clothes.

229
00:19:48,830 --> 00:19:50,720
It was all to steal my fingerprints

230
00:19:50,790 --> 00:19:51,640
to impersonate me.

231
00:19:53,070 --> 00:19:55,270
All to steal our confidential documents.

232
00:19:56,550 --> 00:19:58,310
If Mr. Ji hadn't told me,

233
00:19:59,350 --> 00:20:00,830
I would've been completely fooled.

234
00:20:10,750 --> 00:20:12,030
You set this trap.

235
00:20:30,720 --> 00:20:32,310
How many times did I warn you?

236
00:20:33,800 --> 00:20:35,030
I told you not to cause trouble.

237
00:20:35,110 --> 00:20:37,070
Don't cross Councilman Zhu and Miss Zhu.

238
00:20:38,030 --> 00:20:39,830
I said I would let you go.

239
00:20:39,920 --> 00:20:41,160
As long as you behaved.

240
00:20:42,300 --> 00:20:43,350
I already gave you your freedom.

241
00:20:43,350 --> 00:20:45,000
Why are you still doing this?

242
00:20:51,440 --> 00:20:52,680
Let me go?

243
00:20:53,850 --> 00:20:55,240
Do you think the blood debts
of my family

244
00:20:55,590 --> 00:20:57,110
and my adoptive father,

245
00:20:57,270 --> 00:20:58,480
Xiaocui's eyes,

246
00:20:58,530 --> 00:21:00,030
and the lives of those innocent people

247
00:21:00,110 --> 00:21:01,480
can just be wiped clean?

248
00:21:02,880 --> 00:21:03,720
I stayed

249
00:21:04,400 --> 00:21:07,030
just to see you get cuffed,

250
00:21:07,880 --> 00:21:09,110
and to watch you all

251
00:21:09,440 --> 00:21:10,750
pay for what you've done.

252
00:21:14,440 --> 00:21:15,720
Guan Renjie died.

253
00:21:16,720 --> 00:21:17,920
And Zhou Ziheng showed up.

254
00:21:18,960 --> 00:21:19,830
A reporter died.

255
00:21:20,000 --> 00:21:21,550
And cops A, B, C, D showed up.

256
00:21:21,680 --> 00:21:23,400
I think you deserve to die the most!

257
00:21:36,510 --> 00:21:37,880
I won't protect her anymore.

258
00:21:39,120 --> 00:21:40,350
Do whatever you want with her.

259
00:22:08,270 --> 00:22:09,240
In ancient times,

260
00:22:09,750 --> 00:22:11,030
there was a femme fatale.

261
00:22:11,210 --> 00:22:12,240
Her name was Yang Yuhuan.

262
00:22:13,200 --> 00:22:14,040
I heard

263
00:22:14,200 --> 00:22:16,550
she was suffocated alive in a coffin.

264
00:22:17,790 --> 00:22:19,070
You're also a femme fatale.

265
00:22:20,110 --> 00:22:21,790
So you'll die the same way.

266
00:22:24,880 --> 00:22:25,790
At least Yang Yuhuan

267
00:22:26,440 --> 00:22:28,590
had people cry for her at Mawei Slope.

268
00:22:30,590 --> 00:22:32,640
When you're no longer useful,

269
00:22:33,510 --> 00:22:35,270
those beats

270
00:22:36,000 --> 00:22:37,880
won't leave a trace of you!

271
00:22:40,920 --> 00:22:41,760
You lunatic!

272
00:22:41,880 --> 00:22:42,750
Someone, drag her out!

273
00:22:50,030 --> 00:22:50,870
Don't touch me!

274
00:22:57,480 --> 00:22:59,510
They say Ji Zhijie's woman

275
00:22:59,640 --> 00:23:01,070
is the most beautiful.

276
00:23:01,510 --> 00:23:02,350
Who goes first?

277
00:23:02,960 --> 00:23:04,200
How about together?

278
00:23:04,440 --> 00:23:05,280
Alright, let's go.

279
00:23:18,720 --> 00:23:20,200
So pretty.

280
00:23:30,310 --> 00:23:31,590
Gorgeous.

281
00:23:40,510 --> 00:23:41,350
Me first!

282
00:23:42,750 --> 00:23:43,790
You rascal.

283
00:23:47,160 --> 00:23:49,240
Didn't expect a free treat.

284
00:23:49,590 --> 00:23:50,830
Let's undress her first.

285
00:23:53,350 --> 00:23:54,190
I'll go first.

286
00:24:08,020 --> 00:24:12,780
♪Don't take amber from my eyes♪

287
00:24:14,660 --> 00:24:18,780
♪I'm scared you'll be swallowed by dark♪

288
00:24:20,220 --> 00:24:22,540
♪Watching you get tied down♪

